Description: AcreetionOS Media Writer - Write AcreetionOS images to portable drives
 A tool to create a bootable live USB drive with an edition of AcreetionOS.
 It can automatically download the required image and write it to a USB
 flash drive. Also supports restoring the drive back to normal afterwards.
 .
 Based on Fedora Media Writer by the Fedora Project.
